description:
Danny recaps the season 12 premiere of the greatest show of all time, The Real Housewives of New York. We meet Leah McSweeney, go boxing with Tins, watch Sonja flirt, throw a party with Dorinda, witness a Ramona monologue for the ages, and see a "Lu and improved" Lu.


For tickets to the Chicago live show: https://bit.ly/3bc6QLX

*To support this pod & access bonus episodes, visit Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
